<h1>Styling a Path</h1>

<p>Paths can be styled using strokeColor, strokeWidth, and fillColor.  These values can be set individually or in a style object.  The members of the object are all optional.</p>
<pre>
var circle1 = new Path.Circle(new Point(50, 50), 40)
circle1.strokeColor = 'black'
circle1.fillColor = 'green'
circle1.strokeWidth = 5

var circle2 = new Path.Circle(new Point(200,50), 40)
var style = {
  strokeColor: 'green',
  fillColor: 'black',
  strokeWidth: 10
}
circle2.style = style
</pre>
